---
title: Panko-Crusted Barramundi 'n' Chips with Tartar Sauce and Slaw
description: This dish combines a few different styles of fish 'n' chips to create the best of all! Spiced, crusted fish with creamy slaw, crispy potatoes and zesty tartar sauce for dipping is sure to call back memories of your favourite pub!
